g.text: A scene in near orbit. Slowly, a beautiful ship comes into view from off screen. The camera pans all around it as we see the majesty of this incredible triumph of human inginuity. Themusic swells and the heroic nature of the undertaking is felt. Then as it leaves, propelled atunfathomable speeds, a more poignant and then uncertain sense of awe pervades as we pan out to the twinkling stars and mysteries that await.
